== PURPOSE

Develop operational and technical fluency in how modern fighter electronic warfare (EW) systems generate, prioritize, and present threat information to pilots, and identify PVI design constraints and failure modes (attention capture, nuisance, ambiguity, mis-prioritization, loss of trust).

This is synthesis-driven, not a systematic review.

